com.saptarshidebnath.lib.processrunner.model

Class OutputRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.saptarshidebnath.lib.processrunner.model.OutputRecord

  • public class OutputRecord
extends Object
    Stores each line of output from the Runner. OutputRecord captures the follwoing details : timeStamp, OutputSourceType and the actual output in String format.
